BIBLE TEXT ATTRIBUTION

The Bible text included in this repository is from the Berean Standard Bible (BSB),
which has been dedicated to the public domain. Our paragraph formatting and
structure of the biblical text is also released into the public domain.

For more information about the Berean Standard Bible, visit: https://berean.bible/
